  "diagram_type": "stateDiagram",
  "code": "\nstateDiagram-v2\n    [HealthTech_EMR_Sync] --> Idle\n    Idle --> Gated : Session/day filters & range gate pass\n    Gated --> SignalCheck : Close[HealthTech_EMR_Sync] vs Close[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]\n    SignalCheck --> EntryBUY : Close[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer] >= Close[HealthTech_PatientRecords] AND no SELLs\n    SignalCheck --> EntrySELL : Close[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer] < Close[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault] AND no BUYs\n    EntryBUY --> BasketManage\n    EntrySELL --> BasketManage\n    BasketManage --> AddMore : |price - last_entry| >= Step AND count < MaxTrades\n    AddMore --> BasketManage\n    BasketManage --> SyncTP : compute avg price; set TP = avg ± TP_pts\n    SyncTP --> Idle\n    Idle --> EquityStop : floating P/L < 0 AND |P/L| > (HealthTech_EMR_Sync)\n    Idle --> HiddenTP : Hidden_TP basket profit reached\n    Idle --> DailyTarget : Use_Daily_Target and daily ≥ Daily_Target\n    EquityStop --> Flat\n    HiddenTP --> Flat\n    DailyTarget --> Flat\n    Flat --> Idle\n",
