  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为HealthTech EMR同步模块设计一个完整的状态机。起点是HealthTech_EMR_Sync，然后进入一个Idle空闲状态，等待交易会话启动。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Idle是初始等待状态。那从Idle出来需要什么条件？是直接进入交易吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不是直接交易，要先经过一个Gated门控状态。需要满足会话过滤和区间门控条件才能通过，比如检查是否在允许的交易时段内。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Gated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Idle到Gated的转移条件我记为\"Session/day filters & range gate pass\"。Gated之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Gated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Gated之后进入SignalCheck信号检测状态。这里要比较HealthTech_EMR_Sync的收盘价和HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine的收盘价，判断趋势方向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Gated",
        "SignalCheck",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，SignalCheck的触发条件是Close[HealthTech_EMR_Sync] vs Close[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]的比较，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SignalCheck",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对。SignalCheck之后有两个分支：EntryBUY和EntrySELL。买入条件是HealthTech_LabAnalyzer的收盘价等于HealthTech_PatientRecords的收盘价，且当前没有SELL持仓；卖出条件是HealthTech_LabAnalyzer收盘价低于HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault的收盘价，且没有BUY持仓。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SignalCheck",
        "EntryBUY",
        "EntrySELL",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加EntryBUY和EntrySELL两个状态。无论买入还是卖出，接下来都应该进入持仓管理吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EntryBUY",
        "EntrySELL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，都进入BasketManage篮子管理状态。这里可以加仓，条件是价格与上次入场价的差值等于Step步长，且交易次数小于MaxTrades。加仓后回到BasketManage。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EntryBUY",
        "EntrySELL",
        "BasketManage",
        "AddMore"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "AddMore到BasketManage的循环我理解了。那什么时候退出BasketManage？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BasketManage",
        "AddMore"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "当不再加仓时，进入SyncTP同步止盈状态。计算平均持仓价格，然后设置止盈价位为均价加减TP_pts点数。完成后回到Idle等待下一次机会。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BasketManage",
        "SyncTP",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "SyncTP到Idle的主流程已画好。不过Idle状态还需要考虑风险退出机制吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SyncTP",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，Idle有三个退出路径：EquityStop权益止损，条件是浮动盈亏小于0且亏损绝对值触及阈值；HiddenTP隐藏止盈，当Hidden_TP篮子利润达标；还有DailyTarget日度目标，如果启用日度目标且当日收益已达标。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "EquityStop",
        "HiddenTP",
        "DailyTarget"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认EquityStop的触发条件包含HealthTech_EMR_Sync的引用，其他两个是Hidden_TP和Use_Daily_Target标志。这三个状态之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EquityStop",
        "HiddenTP",
        "DailyTarget",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这三个都进入Flat平仓状态，表示当前无持仓。然后Flat再回到Idle，形成完整的循环。",
